OL,3,C'It's not a death sentence': More
OL,4,Ceducation is needed on HIV and AIDS
OL,6,FA Jersey counsellor says there's a "40-
OL,7,Fyear knowledge gap" about HIV
OL,8,Ftransmission and treatment on the
OL,9,Fisland.
OL,11,FJames Videgrain, from Liberate Jersey,
OL,12,Fsays that stigmas arising from the
OL,13,FAIDS crisis in the 1980s continue to
OL,14,Fplague people's understanding of the
OL,15,Fdisease today.
OL,17,FJames made his comments at a training
OL,18,Fsession hosted by the island's LGBT+
OL,19,Fequality and diversity charity to
OL,20,Fcommemorate World AIDS Day (Sunday 1
OL,21,FDecember).
