OL,3,C'It's not a death sentence': More
OL,4,Ceducation is needed on HIV and AIDS
OL,6,FThe talk was hosted as part of
OL,7,FLiberate's HIV education programme
OL,8,Fwhich is designed to debunk myths
OL,9,Fabout what it's like to live with HIV
OL,10,F- the virus that causes AIDS - in 2024.
OL,12,FThe session also provided information
OL,13,Fabout how to prevent HIV transmission,
OL,14,Fhow HIV is treated today, how it can
OL,15,Fbecome untransmittable, and where
OL,16,Fpeople can go for testing and support.
OL,18,FLiberate hopes this kind of education
OL,19,Fwill prevent the prejudice and
OL,20,Fdiscrimination still suffered by HIV-
OL,21,Fpositive people in the workplace.
