OL,3,C'It's not a death sentence': More
OL,4,Ceducation is needed on HIV and AIDS
OL,6,FJames says: "People still think HIV is
OL,7,Fa death sentence. People are quite
OL,8,Ffearful about how infectious people
OL,9,Fare and how it's transmitted.
OL,11,F"People's knowledge has not
OL,12,Fnecessarily been updated since the
OL,13,F1980s when they saw those tombstone
OL,14,Fadverts on TV.
OL,16,F"Actually, we're in such a different
OL,17,Fplace. You can't pass on the virus
OL,18,Fonce you're on effective treatment,
OL,19,Fyou can have completely normal
OL,20,Frelationships.
