OL,3,C'It's not a death sentence': More
OL,4,Ceducation is needed on HIV and AIDS
OL,6,F"It's not a death sentence - you live
OL,7,Fa normal lifespan. "
OL,9,FJames adds that educating people in
OL,10,FJersey will reduce their fear levels
OL,11,Fand reduce stigma and discrimination.
OL,13,FHe also says the best way to prevent
OL,14,Fthe virus is for people of all sexual
OL,15,Forientations to ensure they are being
OL,16,Fregularly tested for the virus.
